node.title: Diver reported missing at East Cape, Te Araroa
node.description: A search is underway for a diver reported missing in Te Araroa on the East Coast this morning.
node.content:
["A search is underway for a diver reported missing in Te Araroa on the East Coast this morning.", "", "
East Cape Road, Te Araroa, where a diver was reported missing on 29 December, 2021. Photo: Google Maps
", "Police said the scuba diver failed to resurface from where they were, near 566 East Cape Road.", "The diver was reported missing about 10.30am and sea, ground, and air searches are now underway."]
